name: Customizable Plates
description:
Material: Silver or Gold 

Font: Typewriter, Cursive, or Block 

Each plate is handcraft and hammered for an earthy organic feel. Each  plate is made to fit the name, so each plate will be a different length.

Please provide the name that you wish to appear on your plate in Paypal's note to seller section at checkout.

Please allow 14-21 business days for processing and shipping.

Plate orders can not be canceled once order is placed.
